  {
    q: "How often should I get my Hoshizaki ice machine cleaned?",
    a: "LA hard water is aggressive. Our recommendation: descale every 6 months in moderate-volume kitchens, quarterly in 24-hour operations or hotels, and replace pre-filter cartridges every 6 months regardless. If your ice tastes off, if the cubes are cloudy, or if production has dropped, the cleaning interval has been stretched too far. We handle descaling, sanitizing, water-filter replacement, and condenser cleaning on regular maintenance schedules."
